name: You Should Meet in the CBO Suite

affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent:
Reading Time:  < 1 minuteThe Southeastern Live Well Center is home to a wide range of county services all under one roof.
It is also a place for community, collaboration and engagement.
On the first floor of the building, next to the Family Resource Center, a Community Based Organizations (CBO) Suite is available to local groups who serve the community.
The workspace is free to use and an ideal location for organizations that don’t have a budget for a permanent office.
Visit the Southeastern Live Well Center CBO webpage for information on making a reservation.
